🔧 Installation Steps

1. *Initialize your project:*

   ```bash
   mkdir whatsapp-bot
   cd whatsapp-bot
   npm init -y
   ```

2. *Install dependencies:*

   ```bash
   npm install @whiskeysockets/baileys pino qrcode-terminal
   ```

